[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/flamethrower">Flamethrower</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/flamethrower">Flamethrower</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The foe is scorched with an intense blast of fire. The target may also be left with a burn.</p>